<td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;padding-top:40px"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="none" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px"><tr><td align="center" valign="top" style="padding:0;Margin:0;width:560px"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px"><tr><td align="center" class="es-m-txt-c" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><h1 style="Margin:0;line-height:46px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:46px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#cdd6f4"><strong>We're sorry to see you go. See you soon in purr.</strong></h1></td></tr> <tr>
<td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px">Hello {{ $name }},</p></td></tr><tr><td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px">We are saddened to learn that you have decided to leave our community at <strong>purr.</strong> We hope that the time you spent with us was enjoyable and filled with memorable feline moments.</p></td></tr> <tr>
<td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px"><strong>We Value Your Feedback</strong><br>We regret your decision to leave us and would love to understand your reasons better. Any feedback you can share will be extremely valuable in helping us improve and adapt <strong>purr.</strong> to meet the needs of all cat lovers. If you wish to share your reasons or suggestions, we encourage you to respond directly to this email.</p></td></tr> <tr>
<td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px"><strong>Your Feline Friends Will Miss You</strong><br>It’s not just us; the kitties of <strong>purr.</strong> will feel your absence too. You will always be a part of the memories you created here and the shared moments that brightened many days.</p></td></tr> <tr>
<td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px"><strong>You’re Always Welcome Here</strong><br>Remember, you are always welcome at <strong>purr.</strong> If you decide to return in the future and create new memories with the feline community, simply create a new account and join us again.</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr> <tr><td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;padding-bottom:40px"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="none" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px"><tr>
<td align="center" valign="top" style="padding:0;Margin:0;width:560px"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" role="presentation" style="mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px"><tr><td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px"><p style="Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:none;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px">Thank you for having been a part of <strong>purr. </strong>We hope our paths cross again in the future. Wishing you the best in your next adventures!</p> </td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
